_json.gridTitle: Welcome to My Kitchen: A Tour of My New Home - Nell Hill's
_json.description: When Dan and I downsized and moved into our little home by the lake, we had to rethink how we use so many of our spaces, the biggest one being our kitchen and dining areas â€¦. In our Atchison home, we had a kitchen and breakfast nook, separated from the formal dining room by a swinging door. We could entertain large groups in the dining room, and no one ever had to see the horrific mess in the kitchen. Now, there are no secrets. Our snug galley kitchen opens right into our cozy dining area...
